post_content.caption: Debris field from Baltimore bridge collapse is 'very dangerous' for divers: Tiburon Subsea CEO
post_content.description:
Families of those lost in the Baltimore bridge collapse are speaking out. NBC News' Jay Gray and Tiburon Subsea CEO Tim Taylor discuss the tragedy and the search and recovery efforts.
